  "compared_baselines": "The study compares performance across various LLMs, including proprietary models (GPT-4, GPT-3.5-turbo), open-source models (Llama2 7B, 13B, 70B, Vicuna-13B), and medical domain-specific models (PMC-Llama-13B). It also compares results based on two attack methods: prompt-based attacks (PE) and fine-tuning-based attacks (FT).",
